race.comment: PLEADEEL (4) struggled in town this preparation and comes back a few grades today after finishing a poor fifteenth over 2000m at Doomben in BM70 class. Placed here and strips much fitter. KATERINI (9) went back from the sticky draw when jumped in trip for an even eighth over 2400m at the Sunshine Coast. No shock to see her put her best foot forward today. KALKANLI (3) Impending gelding who finished runner-up again when he stalked the speed for a tenacious second over 2110m at Lismore. Up in trip and stays in the mix. TORTILLA (7) broke a long drought last time when he scored by 2.5 lengths at Lismore over 2110m. Chance to go on with it.
